{"tid":1454772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【危險！全部人先離開】機管局：航班登記服務暫停 今日所有航班全部取消","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:39:15.000Z","uid":44358,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"733e2da595d9c62d155592da737a002b08439efa","tid":1454772,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"【1555】機管局再表示，受機場集會影響，所有航班登記服務須即時暫停。除已完成航班登機程序的離港航班，以及正前往香港的抵港航班外，其餘今日所有航班已全部取消。機場現場亦有廣播表示，所有航班即時取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922119&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=190fa711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922119&h=7bb5272c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922119</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n請各巴絲先行離開，飛機日日有升降，明天繼續接機。<br />\n<br />\nＢＥ　ＷＡＴＥＲ，香港重有好多野，等住大家拯救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ade342f131a778f9529bbba4d1a8241a390bb4e3","tid":1454772,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1364f6bb104a76f7ed7bca9b60d3099b59378dc","tid":1454772,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"盡快通知身邊朋友，一定要閃呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass